  <brief_title>A Long-Term Study of Healthy Adults Vaccinated With One Dose of Smallpox Vaccine (LISTER Strain)</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Long-Term Safety and Immunogenicity Follow-up of Healthy Adults Vaccinated With One Dose of Smallpox Vaccine (LISTER Strain)</official_title>
